Package net.usikkert.kouinject.beandata

Contains classes describing the meta-data necessary to create and do injection in beans.

See:
          Description

Interface Summary
InjectionPoint This interface represents an injection point like a method or a field.
 

Class Summary
BeanData This class describes the bean meta-data needed to instantiate a new bean to a consistent state.
BeanKey Represents a bean key for acquiring a real bean instance or the bean data required to create an instance.
CollectionBeanKey A BeanKey for representing a request for a collection of beans.
CollectionProviderBeanKey A BeanKey for representing a request for a CollectionProvider of beans.
ConstructorData Meta-data describing the dependencies for a constructor.
FieldData Meta-data describing the dependency for a field.
MethodData Meta-data describing the dependencies for a method.
ProviderBeanKey A BeanKey for representing request for a Provider.
 

Package net.usikkert.kouinject.beandata Description

Contains classes describing the meta-data necessary to create and do injection in beans.
